      <title>亚马逊投资者关注现金储备不断膨胀且股价接近历史最高纪录</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/amazon-investors-eye-swelling-cash-pile-with-stock-near-record</link>
      <description><![CDATA[多年来，亚马逊公司一直是科技巨头中向股东返还资金最吝啬的。现在，它产生了如此多的现金，以至于华尔街的一些人预计会获得更丰厚的回报。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/amazon-investors-eye-swelling-cash-pile-with-stock-near-record</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 11:07:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃塞俄比亚证券交易所收到两倍于所发行股票的报价</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/ethiopian-stock-exchange-gets-bids-for-twice-the-shares-on-offer</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃塞俄比亚证券交易所表示，随着这个非洲之角国家的交易所筹集资金开始运营，它收到的出价是其向投资者提供的股票的两倍多。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/ethiopian-stock-exchange-gets-bids-for-twice-the-shares-on-offer</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 11:07:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>KISS 歌曲目录以超过 3 亿美元的价格出售给 Pophouse</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-04/kiss-song-catalog-sold-to-pophouse-for-over-300-million-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摇滚乐队 KISS 正在将其歌曲目录出售给 Pophouse Entertainment Group AB，交易价值超过 3 亿美元，其中还包括乐队的名称、形象和肖像。查理·威尔斯在彭博电视台进行报道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-04/kiss-song-catalog-sold-to-pophouse-for-over-300-million-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 10:57:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
