      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 10:20:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度小盘股在 800 亿美元暴跌后数周内卷土重来</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/india-smallcaps-recoup-losses-sparked-by-regulator-s-froth-alert</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度小盘股的一个关键指标收复了监管机构对市场泡沫的担忧引发的长达一个月的损失，因为股市崩盘为投资者提供了逢低买入的机会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/india-smallcaps-recoup-losses-sparked-by-regulator-s-froth-alert</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 04:02:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>挪威1.5万亿美元基金引发力拓对巴西矿山的担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/norway-s-1-5-trillion-fund-raises-concerns-with-rio-over-mine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[挪威1.5万亿美元主权财富基金的道德顾问向力拓集团提出了对巴西一座矿山对环境影响的担忧，再次引发对该基金作为该公司投资者的未来角色的质疑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/norway-s-1-5-trillion-fund-raises-concerns-with-rio-over-mine</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 18:05:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴黎俱乐部将埃塞俄比亚与国际货币基金组织的交易期限延长至六月</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/paris-club-said-to-extend-ethiopia-s-imf-deal-deadline-to-june</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据称，主要由发达国家债权人组成的巴黎俱乐部已将埃塞俄比亚与国际货币基金组织达成初步救助协议的最后期限延长三个月至六月底。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/paris-club-said-to-extend-ethiopia-s-imf-deal-deadline-to-june</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 17:54:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
