      <title>欧洲联盟考虑出售少数股权，选择LionTree</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/euroleague-taps-liontree-as-it-explores-sale-of-minority-stake</link>
      <description><![CDATA[首席执行官保利乌斯·莫蒂尤纳斯 (Paulius Motiejunas) 表示，欧洲顶级男子职业篮球联赛欧洲联盟正在探索通过出售少数股权来筹集资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/euroleague-taps-liontree-as-it-explores-sale-of-minority-stake</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 17:33:29 GMT</pubDate>
